<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Gargi Singh — Curri</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --yellow:#FFD000;--yellow-dark:#C9A800;
  --ink:#0C0C0C;--ink-2:#161616;--ink-3:#1F1F1F;
  --white:#FFFFFF;--off:#F5F5F0;
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  --muted:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  --orange:#FF6B00;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;background:var(--ink);color:var(--white);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}
.caution{height:36px;background:repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,var(--yellow) 0px,var(--yellow) 20px,var(--ink) 20px,var(--ink) 40px);width:100%;flex-shrink:0}
.caution.thin{height:8px}
.cursor{width:10px;height:10px;background:var(--yellow);border-radius:0;position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(45deg);transition:width .15s,height .15s}
body{cursor:none}
@media(max-width:768px){body{cursor:auto}.cursor{display:none}}
nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:var(--ink);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.caution.thin{position:relative;top:0}
.nav-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:52px;padding:0 2rem}
.nav-logo{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--yellow)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;list-style:none}
.nav-links a{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--yellow)}
.nav-cta{background:var(--yellow);color:var(--ink)!important;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:2px;font-size:12px!important;font-weight:700!important}
.wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.reveal-left{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-24px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.reveal-left.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}
.reveal-right{opacity:0;transform:translateX(24px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.reveal-right.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}
.d1{transition-delay:.1s}.d2{transition-delay:.2s}.d3{transition-delay:.3s}.d4{transition-delay:.4s}
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:grid;grid-template-rows:auto 1fr auto;background:var(--ink);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,208,0,0.04) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,208,0,0.04) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:48px 48px;pointer-events:none}
.hero-top-tape{background:repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,var(--yellow) 0,var(--yellow) 20px,var(--ink) 20px,var(--ink) 40px);height:36px}
.hero-content{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:0 2rem 3rem;position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;width:100%}
.hero-eyebrow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:2rem}
.hero-badge{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--yellow);border:1px solid rgba(255,208,0,0.25);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:2px}
.hero-dot{width:8px;height:8px;background:var(--yellow);border-radius:0;animation:blink 1.5s infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.2}}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(52px,8.5vw,112px);font-weight:700;line-height:.9;letter-spacing:-4px;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:2rem;text-transform:uppercase}
.hero h1 .y{color:var(--yellow)}
.hero h1 .stroke{-webkit-text-stroke:1.5px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);color:transparent}
.hero-bottom{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:2rem;align-items:end}
.hero-desc{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.hero-desc strong{color:var(--white);font-weight:600}
.hero-stats-row{display:flex;gap:2rem;justify-content:center}
.hs{text-align:center}
.hs .num{font-size:44px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-2px;display:block}
.hs .num sub{font-size:20px;color:var(--yellow)}
.hs .label{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px;display:block}
.hero-actions{text-align:right;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.75rem;align-items:flex-end}
.btn-y{background:var(--yellow);color:var(--ink);padding:12px 24px;border-radius:2px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:transform .15s}
.btn-y:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
.btn-w{background:transparent;color:var(--white);padding:12px 24px;border-radius:2px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;border:1px solid var(--border);letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:border-color .2s}
.btn-w:hover{border-color:var(--yellow);color:var(--yellow)}
.ticker{background:var(--yellow);padding:.55rem 0;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap}
.ticker-track{display:inline-block;animation:scroll 20s linear infinite}
.ticker-track span{font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 2rem}
.ticker-track span::before{content:'▶';margin-right:1.5rem;font-size:8px;opacity:.5}
@keyframes scroll{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
section{padding:6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sec-eye{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--yellow);margin-bottom:.75rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.sec-eye::before{content:'';width:20px;height:2px;background:var(--yellow)}
.sec-title{font-size:clamp(28px,4.5vw,48px);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1.5px;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase}
.sec-intro{font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:3rem;max-width:560px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.match-stack{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.match-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border)}
.mc{background:var(--ink-2);padding:2rem}
.mc.hl{background:rgba(255,208,0,0.05);border-left:3px solid var(--yellow)}
.mc-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.6rem}
.mc.hl .mc-label{color:var(--yellow)}
.mc-req{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:.4rem}
.mc.hl .mc-req{color:var(--white)}
.mc-proof{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);line-height:1.65;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.mc.hl .mc-proof{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)}
.built-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:1px}
.b-card{background:var(--ink-2);padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:background .2s}
.b-card:hover{background:var(--ink-3)}
.b-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%;background:var(--border)}
.b-card.y::after{background:var(--yellow)}.b-card.o::after{background:var(--orange)}
.b-num{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.75rem}
.b-card.y .b-num{color:var(--yellow)}.b-card.o .b-num{color:var(--orange)}
.b-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.b-body{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);line-height:1.65;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.b-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;margin-top:.75rem;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.tag-live{background:rgba(255,208,0,0.1);color:rgba(255,208,0,0.7);border:1px solid rgba(255,208,0,0.15)}
.tag-build{background:rgba(255,107,0,0.1);color:rgba(255,107,0,0.7);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,0,0.15)}
.tag-stealth{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}
.force-strip{background:var(--ink-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:1rem}
.force-head{padding:2rem 2.5rem 1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:1.5rem}
.force-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--yellow)}
.force-title{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);letter-spacing:-.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.force-cells{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
.fc{padding:1.5rem 2rem;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
.fc:last-child{border-right:none}
.fc-v{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);line-height:1;margin-bottom:.4rem;text-transform:uppercase}
.fc:hover .fc-v{color:var(--yellow)}
.fc-d{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);line-height:1.4;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.why-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.wc{background:var(--ink-2);padding:2.5rem;transition:background .2s}
.wc:hover{background:var(--ink-3)}.wc.y{background:var(--yellow)}
.wc-title{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.5rem;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-.3px;text-transform:uppercase}
.wc.y .wc-title{color:var(--ink)}
.wc-body{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.7;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.wc.y .wc-body{color:rgba(0,0,0,0.6)}
.progress-section{background:var(--ink-2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:4rem 0}
.progress-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:2.5rem}
.bar-row{margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.bar-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.bar-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--white)}
.bar-pct{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--yellow)}
.bar-track{height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:0;overflow:hidden}
.bar-fill{height:100%;background:var(--yellow);border-radius:0;width:0;transition:width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)}
.tl{position:relative}
.tl::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:88px;top:8px;bottom:0;width:1px;background:var(--border)}
.tl-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr;gap:0 2rem;margin-bottom:0}
.tl-date{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:700;padding-top:4px;text-align:right;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.tl-right{padding:0 0 2.5rem 2rem;position:relative}
.tl-right::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:-5px;top:6px;width:10px;height:10px;background:var(--ink);border:2px solid var(--border);transform:rotate(45deg)}
.tl-item:first-child .tl-right::before{background:var(--yellow);border-color:var(--yellow)}
.tl-role{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:2px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:-.3px}
.tl-org{font-size:12px;color:var(--yellow);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:.5rem;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}
.tl-body{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);line-height:1.7;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.tl-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-top:.6rem}
.tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.tag-y{background:rgba(255,208,0,0.08);color:rgba(255,208,0,0.7);border:1px solid rgba(255,208,0,0.15)}
.tag-o{background:rgba(255,107,0,0.08);color:rgba(255,107,0,0.6);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,0,0.12)}
.tag-w{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}
.contact-sec{background:var(--ink);padding:0}
.contact-tape{background:repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,var(--yellow) 0,var(--yellow) 20px,var(--ink) 20px,var(--ink) 40px);height:36px}
.contact-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 2rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center}
.contact-left .sec-title{color:var(--white)}
.contact-left p{font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-top:.75rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
.contact-cards{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.cc{background:var(--ink-2);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;transition:background .2s}
.cc:hover{background:var(--ink-3)}
.cc-l{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px}
.cc-v{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--white)}
.cc-v a{color:var(--white);text-decoration:none}
.cc-arr{font-size:16px;color:var(--border)}
.counter{display:inline-block}
@media(max-width:768px){
  .hero-bottom,.match-row,.built-grid,.force-cells,.why-grid,.contact-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .hero h1{letter-spacing:-2px}.nav-links{display:none}.tl::before{left:68px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="cursor" id="cur"></div>
<nav>
  <div class="caution thin"></div>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#">Gargi <span>Singh</span></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#match">The fit</a></li>
      <li><a href="#built">Built</a></li>
      <li><a href="#why">Why Curri</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Let's talk</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-top-tape"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow reveal">
      <span class="hero-badge">Manager, Operations Strategy · Curri</span>
      <div class="hero-dot"></div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="reveal d1">I don't<br>manage<br><span class="y">teams.</span><br><span class="stroke">I manage</span><br>outcomes.</h1>
    <div class="hero-bottom reveal d2">
      <p class="hero-desc">Product Operations Manager at Bridgetown Research — <strong>founding team, Series A</strong>. I own ambiguous, cross-functional problems end to end. No playbook. No formal authority. Just execution and measurable business impact.</p>
      <div class="hero-stats-row">
        <div class="hs"><span class="num"><span class="counter" data-target="11">0</span><sub>mo</sub></span><span class="label">Associate → Manager</span></div>
        <div class="hs"><span class="num"><span class="counter" data-target="6">0</span><sub>+</sub></span><span class="label">Systems shipped</span></div>
        <div class="hs"><span class="num"><span class="counter" data-target="100">0</span><sub>+</sub></span><span class="label">Live projects</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#match" class="btn-y">See the fit →</a>
        <a href="#built" class="btn-w">What I built</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="ticker">
  <div class="ticker-track">
    <span>Force multiplier for ops leadership</span><span>Drives without formal authority</span><span>Ambiguous problems → measurable outcomes</span><span>Founding team · Series A</span><span>6 systems shipped</span><span>Hired ops team of 4</span><span>Genuine AI fluency</span><span>Data to insight to action</span><span>Force multiplier for ops leadership</span><span>Drives without formal authority</span><span>Ambiguous problems → measurable outcomes</span><span>Founding team · Series A</span><span>6 systems shipped</span><span>Hired ops team of 4</span><span>Genuine AI fluency</span><span>Data to insight to action</span>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="progress-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="progress-title reveal">Operational capability — site assessment</div>
    <div class="bar-row reveal d1"><div class="bar-label"><span class="bar-name">Cross-functional ops ownership</span><span class="bar-pct">100%</span></div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" data-width="100"></div></div></div>
    <div class="bar-row reveal d2"><div class="bar-label"><span class="bar-name">Ambiguous problem → structured execution</span><span class="bar-pct">100%</span></div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" data-width="100"></div></div></div>
    <div class="bar-row reveal d3"><div class="bar-label"><span class="bar-name">Driving without formal authority</span><span class="bar-pct">100%</span></div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" data-width="100"></div></div></div>
    <div class="bar-row reveal d4"><div class="bar-label"><span class="bar-name">Data → insight → action</span><span class="bar-pct">95%</span></div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" data-width="95"></div></div></div>
    <div class="bar-row reveal"><div class="bar-label"><span class="bar-name">AI fluency — builder, not just user</span><span class="bar-pct">90%</span></div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" data-width="90"></div></div></div>
  </div>
</div>
<section id="match">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-eye reveal">Role fit</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal d1">Curri's JD.<br>My last 14 months.</h2>
    <p class="sec-intro reveal d2">Line by line. Every requirement in this JD maps directly to what I've been doing at Bridgetown — without being asked, without a playbook, and without a team above me.</p>
    <div class="match-stack reveal d1">
      <div class="match-row">
        <div class="mc"><div class="mc-label">Curri needs</div><div class="mc-req">Own & drive highest-priority cross-functional ops initiatives end-to-end</div><div class="mc-proof">Individual contributor who manages outcomes, not people. Extension of Ops leadership.</div></div>
        <div class="mc hl"><div class="mc-label">I've done this</div><div class="mc-req">Every system at Bridgetown — all 6 — started as a gap I spotted and owned end-to-end</div><div class="mc-proof">No hierarchy. No handoffs. From identifying the gap to making the case to leadership to shipping and running it — that's been my entire operating model for 14 months. Autopublish, vendor dashboard, selection framework, pre-approval feature, team ops, stealth vertical — all mine.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="match-row">
        <div class="mc"><div class="mc-label">Curri needs</div><div class="mc-req">Identify operational gaps & solve creatively — not by adding headcount or producing more decks</div><div class="mc-proof">Rethink how the work gets done. Force multiplier, not incrementalist.</div></div>
        <div class="mc hl"><div class="mc-label">I've done this</div><div class="mc-req">Built autopublish — replaced manual review entirely with 3 automated signals</div><div class="mc-proof">Fraud detection + quality scoring + identity verification. Every time my team was doing something a system could do, I built the system. No headcount added. No deck produced. The workflow was rethought and replaced. That's the instinct Curri is describing.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="match-row">
        <div class="mc"><div class="mc-label">Curri needs</div><div class="mc-req">Lead ops goal setting, KPI definition, reporting & business reviews</div><div class="mc-proof">Partner with Product, Engineering, Finance, Sales. Provide analysis & updates to executive leadership.</div></div>
        <div class="mc hl"><div class="mc-label">I've done this</div><div class="mc-req">Work directly with founder & Strategy PM — all OKRs, reporting, and strategic decisions run through me</div><div class="mc-proof">Set OKRs for my team of 4. Built the ops dashboard tracking 100+ live projects. Surface quality signals and performance data to leadership. Cross-functional coordination across product, ops, vendors, and clients — no middleman, no translation layer.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="match-row">
        <div class="mc"><div class="mc-label">Curri needs</div><div class="mc-req">Proven track record of driving execution without formal authority</div><div class="mc-proof">Insatiably curious. Data to insight to action fast. Strong operational judgment.</div></div>
        <div class="mc hl"><div class="mc-label">I've done this</div><div class="mc-req">Series A, no hierarchy — every initiative was unsolicited and driven purely through influence</div><div class="mc-proof">None of the 6 systems I built were requested. I spotted the gap, made the case, and drove execution across functions with no formal authority over any of them. Promoted in 11 months for exactly this. That's not a claim — it's the promotion itself.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="built" style="background:var(--ink-2)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-eye reveal">What I built</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal d1">Six systems.<br>Zero headcount added.<br>All live.</h2>
    <p class="sec-intro reveal d2">Not decks. Not recommendations. Systems that run. Each one started as an ambiguous gap — exactly what Curri is hiring for.</p>
    <div class="built-grid">
